Each layer is a Java class:
- class Controller { ... } вҶ’ handles HTTP, has an object of Service
- class Service { Service() { ... } } вҶ’ business logic
- Repo вҶ’ talks to DB

Key insight: Each layer depends on the next вҖ” Spring injects these dependencies automatically using `@Autowired`, so you never manually `new` them.

